### Aegis lineup API — stages, slots, sets
### Run with REST Client extension. Replace cookie after sign-in.

@host = http://localhost:3000
@cookie = better-auth.session_token=...replace_after_signin...

### ── Stages (global, not per-edition) ──────────────────────────────

### List stages
GET {{host}}/api/stages
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Create stage — success
POST {{host}}/api/stages
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "name": "Beach", "slug": "beach", "color": "#7C9EFF", "sortOrder": 4 }

### Create stage — failure: bad slug
POST {{host}}/api/stages
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "name": "X", "slug": "Has Spaces" }

### Create stage — failure: duplicate slug
POST {{host}}/api/stages
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "name": "Main", "slug": "main" }

### Stage one — replace ID
@stageId = REPLACE_WITH_STAGE_ID
GET {{host}}/api/stages/{{stageId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Update stage (partial)
PATCH {{host}}/api/stages/{{stageId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "color": "#16D060" }

### Delete stage
DELETE {{host}}/api/stages/{{stageId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### ── Slots (per edition + stage + day) ─────────────────────────────

### List all slots for current edition
GET {{host}}/api/slots
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### List slots filtered by day
GET {{host}}/api/slots?day=friday
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Create slot — success
POST {{host}}/api/slots
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "stageId": "{{stageId}}",
  "day": "friday",
  "startTime": "22:00",
  "endTime": "23:30"
}

### Create slot — failure: bad time format
POST {{host}}/api/slots
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "stageId": "{{stageId}}",
  "day": "friday",
  "startTime": "10pm",
  "endTime": "11:30"
}

### Create slot — failure: same start and end
POST {{host}}/api/slots
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "stageId": "{{stageId}}",
  "day": "friday",
  "startTime": "22:00",
  "endTime": "22:00"
}

### Slot one — replace ID
@slotId = REPLACE_WITH_SLOT_ID
GET {{host}}/api/slots/{{slotId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Update slot (partial)
PATCH {{host}}/api/slots/{{slotId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "endTime": "00:00" }

### Update slot — failure: empty body
PATCH {{host}}/api/slots/{{slotId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{}

### Delete slot
DELETE {{host}}/api/slots/{{slotId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### ── Sets (artist <-> slot) ────────────────────────────────────────

### List sets for a slot
GET {{host}}/api/sets?slotId={{slotId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### List sets for an artist
@artistId = REPLACE_WITH_ARTIST_ID
GET {{host}}/api/sets?artistId={{artistId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Create set — success
POST {{host}}/api/sets
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "slotId": "{{slotId}}",
  "artistId": "{{artistId}}",
  "status": "option",
  "announceBatch": "Batch 1",
  "feeAmountCents": 250000,
  "feeCurrency": "USD"
}

### Create set — failure: missing slotId/artistId
POST {{host}}/api/sets
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "status": "confirmed" }

### Set one — replace ID
@setId = REPLACE_WITH_SET_ID
GET {{host}}/api/sets/{{setId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Update set — partial: confirm
PATCH {{host}}/api/sets/{{setId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "status": "confirmed" }

### Update set — partial: clear announce batch
PATCH {{host}}/api/sets/{{setId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "announceBatch": "" }

### Delete set
DELETE {{host}}/api/sets/{{setId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}
